statement.title: Problem Description
statement.content: Given an integer N,you should come up with the minimum nonnegative integer M.M meets the follow condition: M2%10x=N (x=0,1,2,3....)

statement.title: Input
statement.content:
The first line has an integer T( T< = 1000), the number of test cases.
For each case, each line contains one integer N(0<= N <=109), indicating the given number.

statement.title: Output
statement.content: For each case output the answer if it exists, otherwise print “None”.
